Add a binding specification for the Analog Devices Inc. AD7625,
AD7626, AD7960, and AD7961 ADCs.

Reviewed-by: Conor Dooley <conor.dooley@microchip.com>
Signed-off-by: Trevor Gamblin <tgamblin@baylibre.com>
